    <item>
      <title>随着央行考虑变革，印度可再生能源可能会变得更加昂贵</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-09/indian-renewables-may-get-costlier-as-central-bank-mulls-changes</link>
      <description><![CDATA[一家顶级咨询公司表示，印度央行的项目融资提议可能会使可再生能源项目的借贷成本增加多达 1 个百分点，从而可能导致该国风电和太阳能发电价格上涨。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-09/indian-renewables-may-get-costlier-as-central-bank-mulls-changes</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 09 May 2024 08:07:27 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>土耳其央行上调通胀前景以制定政策</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-09/turkish-central-bank-raises-inflation-outlook-that-shapes-policy</link>
      <description><![CDATA[土耳其央行上调了年底通胀预期，此举出人意料，突显出该国在将物价增速从目前近 70% 的水平放缓的过程中面临的挑战。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-09/turkish-central-bank-raises-inflation-outlook-that-shapes-policy</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 09 May 2024 08:04:05 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
